{"id": "1408510483522261173", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "247370231821893632", "author_name": "reapersakamaki", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T17:57:48.131000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1408510483291570256", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 435655, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1408510311811645540/1408510483291570256/image.png?ex=6a32375c&is=6a30e5dc&hm=f4ee96bade74c7f2867b0fc98dd1e522a50948b78fada29da5b2f34e28d88e13&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408510783834296483", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "247370231821893632", "author_name": "reapersakamaki", "author_bot": false, "content": "Wheels and Codenames completed, if possible in the wheels some names are quite ambiguous so I would like someone to go over them for proofread.", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T17:58:59.731000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408525250815066143", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "Just glancing at the two screenshots, I'd probably go with \"Devoração Aberrante\" for \"Aberrant Devour,\" \"Modelo Anatômico do Oblívio\" for \"Manikin of Oblivion,\" \"Banquete Sangrento\" for \"Bloody Feast,\" \"Correntes Desvinculadas\" for \"Chains Unbound,\" \"Água Viva Lunar\" for \"Moon Jelly,\" \"Faísca do Mar\" for \"Mareel Glow,\" \"Homem Tique-Toque\" for \"Tick-Tock Man,\" and \"Bailarina da Fogueira\" for \"Balefire Ballerina.\"", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T18:56:28.928000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408526181032268049", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "\"Água Viva\" instead of \"Medusa\" simply because the former is used for the same animal before they've matured into adults, so it fits Aurita more in my opinion.\n\nMareel is a term for the ocean glowing with a bioluminescent bacteria. In Portuguese they're called \"Noctilucas\" and the phenomenon is called \"Faísca do Mar\" so it seems appropriate.\n\nAs for \"Homem Tique-Toque\" I think it's important to be literal here, since it's most likely a reference to Harlan Ellison' short story \"\"Repent, Harlequin!\" Said the Ticktockman.\"", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T19:00:10.709000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408526518858158131", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "Really great work so far. I've been mostly focused on the English side, but I can help here and there with proofreading.", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T19:01:31.253000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408526608008089630", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "Also not a fan of \"A Corredora\" for \"The Scuttler,\" but I'm struggling to come up with something appropriate.", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T19:01:52.508000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408527385132797962", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "It could be a reference to a street gang from the UK in the 1800s. More specifically, \"scuttling\" at the time was the slang for their turf wars. But it's probably just a reference to a \"scuttling rat.”", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T19:04:57.789000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-23T03:53:23.275000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408529196879319083", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "Maybe just \"Tique-Toque\" for Erica's Codename, to make it less silly, but it's tricky.", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T19:12:09.743000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408529540485218494", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 19, "author_id": "247370231821893632", "author_name": "reapersakamaki", "author_bot": false, "content": "Most of the translations would feel awkward and also nor really be translated if left as is, since and some you had to use synonyms for it having the same meaning one word can be translated in multiple ways, like The scuttler translated for Portuguese the one that is 'less bad' is the translation of runner instead of runaway,", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T19:13:31.665000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["352428907468947474"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1408525250815066143", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408530118133026947", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "Scuttling is very often used for small things, such as a rat, scampering quickly. So it's difficult to come up with a proper term for it. I just don't think being literal there works that well.", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T19:15:49.387000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
{"id": "1408530321640788051", "channel_id": "1408510311811645540", "type": 0, "author_id": "247370231821893632", "author_name": "reapersakamaki", "author_bot": false, "content": "Yep thus why finding a word that represents the meaning, but it gets problematic when you don't know which feeling they are representing", "timestamp": "2025-08-22T19:16:37.907000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1408510311811645540", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "PT Contribution", "forum_channel_id": "1408291767207591976"}
